Source code incorporated from package 'coda'
--------------------------------------------------

Several functions have been copied with modification from the R
package 'coda', under the terms of GPL version 3. They are identified
in the source code, along with copyright attribution.


What does this mean?
====================

If you are modifying 'ergm' or adopting any source code from
'ergm' for use in another application, you must ensure that the
copyright and attributions mentioned in the license above appear
in the code of your modified version or application. These 
attributions must also appear when the package is loaded
(e.g., via 'library' or 'require').

